  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide Clean Water to 270 Refugees in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bugema Community Based Child Based Organization plans to provide clean and safe drinking water to 270 refugees who hail from the current civil unrest in South Sudan and Democratic Republic of Congo flooding across the borders into Uganda. This project is working towards saving refugees from suffering from typhoid, malaria, Diarrhoea, cholera and filariasis as a result of drinking dirty water and bathing in dirty water.</narrative>
  </description>
